 be to any parent or relative specified in N.J.A.C. 10:90-2.7(a)3; and 4. Upon return of the child, WFNJ eligibility will exist. (e) EA is also available in cases where only the child is eligible to receive WFNJ cash assistance (that is, the parent-person is non-needy). History

